<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="Aura Compass Pro by Neon Dust Labs. Premium field navigation with compass, bearings, waypoints, tracks, GPX workflows, widgets, and Apple Watch support."
  />
  <title>Aura Compass Pro | Neon Dust Labs</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #04111d;
      --bg-deep: #071a2b;
      --panel: rgba(9, 20, 34, 0.82);
      --panel-strong: rgba(12, 27, 44, 0.92);
      --line: rgba(118, 224, 255, 0.18);
      --line-strong: rgba(118, 224, 255, 0.34);
      --text: #f4f8fd;
      --muted: #aac0d5;
      --accent: #76e0ff;
      --accent-2: #4a94ff;
      --glow: rgba(118, 224, 255, 0.2);
      --shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.34);
      --radius-xl: 32px;
      --radius-lg: 24px;
      --radius-md: 18px;
    }
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Display", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(118, 224, 255, 0.2), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 88% 12%, rgba(74, 148, 255, 0.18), transparent 24%),
        linear-gradient(155deg, var(--bg), var(--bg-deep));
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    a {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    p, li {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .shell {
      width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 40px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 28px 0 72px;
    }
    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(5, 14, 24, 0.62);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
    }
    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      min-width: 0;
    }
    .brand-mark {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.75), transparent 22%),
        linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(118,224,255,0.28), rgba(74,148,255,0.16));
      border: 1px solid var(--line-strong);
      box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.1), 0 10px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
    }
    .brand-copy {
      min-width: 0;
    }
    .brand-copy strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 15px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }
    .brand-copy span {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }
    .nav a {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      height: 38px;
      padding: 0 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--text);
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: 160ms ease;
    }
    .nav a:hover {
      border-color: var(--line);
      background: rgba(118, 224, 255, 0.08);
    }
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 56px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(9,20,34,0.9), rgba(7,17,30,0.78)),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(118,224,255,0.16), transparent 28%);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .hero::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: auto -10% -35% auto;
      width: 420px;
      height: 420px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(118, 224, 255, 0.14), transparent 62%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .eyebrow::before {
      content: "";
      width: 30px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--line-strong);
    }
    h1 {
      max-width: 820px;
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      font-size: clamp(42px, 6vw, 78px);
      line-height: 0.94;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }
    .lead {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .hero-rail {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }
    .pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      height: 38px;
      padding: 0 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(118, 224, 255, 0.07);
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 14px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
    .card {
      padding: 26px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--panel);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    }
    .card h2,
    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .feature-card {
      grid-column: span 4;
    }
    .wide-card {
      grid-column: span 6;
    }
    .metric-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }
    .metric {
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      background: rgba(118, 224, 255, 0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(118, 224, 255, 0.12);
    }
    .metric strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .cta-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 22px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-width: 160px;
      height: 46px;
      padding: 0 20px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: transform 160ms ease, box-shadow 160ms ease, border-color 160ms ease;
    }
    .button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
    .button.primary {
      color: #04111d;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #b0f0ff);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px var(--glow);
    }
    .button.secondary {
      color: var(--text);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(118, 224, 255, 0.06);
    }
    .footer {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 26px;
      padding: 18px 6px 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero {
        padding: 34px 26px;
      }
      .feature-card,
      .wide-card {
        grid-column: span 12;
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .shell {
        width: min(100% - 24px, 1120px);
        padding-top: 14px;
      }
      .topbar {
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 16px;
      }
      .nav {
        width: 100%;
        justify-content: flex-start;
      }
      .metric-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(36px, 11vw, 56px);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="shell">
    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="brand-copy">
          <strong>Aura Compass Pro</strong>
          <span>by Neon Dust Labs</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <nav class="nav" aria-label="Primary">
        <a href="./marketing.html">Overview</a>
        <a href="./support.html">Support</a>
        <a href="./privacy.html">Privacy</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
      <p class="eyebrow">Neon Dust Labs Navigation</p>
      <h1>Field navigation with premium clarity, route awareness, and return confidence.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Aura Compass Pro brings together a live compass, locked bearings, grouped waypoints,
        track analytics, GPX workflows, widgets, and Apple Watch support in one focused tool
        designed for outdoor movement and dependable field use.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-rail">
        <span class="pill">True North + Magnetic North</span>
        <span class="pill">Waypoints + Return to Start</span>
        <span class="pill">GPX Import / Export</span>
        <span class="pill">Widget + Apple Watch</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="button primary" href="./support.html">Get Support</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="./privacy.html">Read Privacy Policy</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="grid">
      <article class="card feature-card">
        <h3>Precision Compass</h3>
        <p>
          Read heading data with a premium instrument-style interface, coordinate formatting,
          and fast switching between true north and magnetic north.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="card feature-card">
        <h3>Guided Navigation</h3>
        <p>
          Save a waypoint, lock a bearing, return to your start point, or follow a route preview
          with compact navigation guidance built for real movement.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="card feature-card">
        <h3>Track Intelligence</h3>
        <p>
          Record sessions with pace, moving time, stopped time, elevation gain/loss,
          and fast session export when you want to archive or share your route.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card wide-card">
        <h2>Why It Feels Pro</h2>
        <p>
          Aura Compass Pro is designed to stay focused. The experience is clean, fast,
          and readable under pressure, with premium theming and streamlined field actions
          instead of cluttered utility menus.
        </p>
        <div class="metric-grid">
          <div class="metric">
            <strong>Coordinate Systems</strong>
            DMS, decimal, UTM, and real MGRS support for users who need more than a basic compass.
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <strong>Shared Surfaces</strong>
            iPhone, widget, and Apple Watch companion keep route context available at a glance.
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <strong>Field Workflows</strong>
            Save Spot, Return to Start, Lock Bearing, and grouped waypoints support real sessions.
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <strong>Export Control</strong>
            GPX import/export and session sharing are always user-initiated and easy to review.
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="card wide-card">
        <h2>Built by Neon Dust Labs</h2>
        <p>
          This app is part of a design-led software approach that values precision, atmosphere,
          and focused tools. If you need help, feature guidance, or launch support, the support
          and privacy pages below are the official public references for store submission.
        </p>
        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="button primary" href="mailto:hello@neondustlabs.com">hello@neondustlabs.com</a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="https://www.neondustlabs.com">Visit Neon Dust Labs</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
      <span>© 2026 Neon Dust Labs. Aura Compass Pro.</span>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="./support.html">Support</a>
        <a href="./privacy.html">Privacy</a>
        <a href="https://www.neondustlabs.com">neondustlabs.com</a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
